Version:     1.5.1
Release:     1%{?dist}
Summary:     The libxo library

Prefix:      /usr

Vendor:      Juniper Networks, Inc.
Packager:    Phil Shafer <phil@juniper.net>
License:     BSD

Group:       Development/Libraries
URL:         https://github.com/Juniper/libxo
